#Day 4
How to setup DevSecOps Pipeline for Amazon EKS with Terraform
Requirements: https://github.com/The-DevSec-Blueprint/aws-devsecops-pipeline
- VSCODE IDE (Use to walk around code)
- GIT (To clone repo from GH)
- Docker (build docker file locally)
- Python (App build runs on)
- Terraform (locally perform TFE plan through CMD / Powershell)
- Snyk CLI (scanning code)

Theory:
https://www.devsecblueprint.com/
Key steps considered here:
1. Concepts You'll Need To Know
2. Building Application DevSecOps Pipelines
3. Building Cloud DevSecOps Pipelines

